FBIS3-12163 "drnes039_l_94014" FBIS-NES-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 ISRAEL Letter of Appointment Issued to Inquiry Commission TA2702191294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1900 GMT 27 Feb 94 TA2702191294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] This evening, the ministerial committee appointed by the cabinet earlier today issued the letter of appointment to the state commission of inquiry which will investigate the massacre in Hebron and reach conclusions about the facts and circumstances pertaining to it. The commission, whose composition will be decided by the president of the Supreme Court, will be entitled to submit conclusions to the government. No time limit has been set for the duration of the commission's work.
